- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on building generative models for language using self-attention and dynamic convolutions. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new approach to improve the performance of machine learning models. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a possible category as self-attention is also used in image generation models. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is another possible category as the paper proposes a new approach to improve the efficiency of neural networks. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a broad category that could also be relevant as the paper proposes a new approach to improve the performance of AI models.
